{
  "text": "A general class of non-extremal dyonic rotating black holes with moduli without NUT charge for this model was found in [CITATION_1] . It was noted there that the black hole entropy S + and the fake \"inner horizon entropy\" S \u2212 , defined as the area of the inner horizon divided by 4G, can be written as",
